Code preview of the table CON_合同条款的频次信息

drop table "CON_TermRhythm" cascade constraints;

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: "CON_TermRhythm" */
/*==============================================================*/
create table "CON_TermRhythm"
(
"TermRhythmID" NUMBER(32) not null,
"ContractID" NUMBER(32) not null,
"SAPContractCode" VARCHAR2(20),
"CompanyCode" VARCHAR2(20) not null,
"EntityCode" VARCHAR2(20) not null,
"TermName" NVARCHAR2(100) not null,
"TermCode" VARCHAR2(10),
"FrequencyNum" INTEGER not null,
"TermType" INTEGER not null,
"FrequencyUnit" NUMBER(10) default 0 not null,
"WeekStart" NUMBER(10) default 7 not null,
"MonthStart" NUMBER(10) default 14 not null,
"ConditionAmount" NUMBER(10) default 0 not null,
"ChangeIndicator" CHAR(1) default 'N' not null,
"SyncSAPflag" INTEGER default 0 not null,
constraint PK_CON_TERMRHYTHM primary key ("TermRhythmID")
);

comment on column "CON_TermRhythm"."TermName" is
'对应SAP的TERM_TEXT';

comment on column "CON_TermRhythm"."TermCode" is
'对应SAP的TERM_NO
默认空，有0010,0020等';

comment on column "CON_TermRhythm"."FrequencyNum" is
'对应SAP的FREQUENCY
除了T开头的条款，其他类均设置为"1",对于T类，如涉及跨期的周期定价，需单独涉及条款编号，并设置为周期频率数';

comment on column "CON_TermRhythm"."TermType" is
'1:合同租金 2:审批优惠
';

comment on column "CON_TermRhythm"."FrequencyUnit" is
'对应SAP的FREQUENCY_UNIT
默认"0" ，按月';

comment on column "CON_TermRhythm"."WeekStart" is
'对应SAP的STARTING_WEEK
默认 7';

comment on column "CON_TermRhythm"."MonthStart" is
'对应SAP的STARTING_MONTH
默认 "14"';

comment on column "CON_TermRhythm"."ConditionAmount" is
'对应SAP的CONDITION_AMOUNT_REF
默认为0 ，按月计租';

comment on column "CON_TermRhythm"."ChangeIndicator" is
'N:初始创建
I:新增
D:删除';
